WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )


00:01:05.828 --> 00:01:08.260
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

00:01:08.388 --> 00:01:11.300
=Episode 23=

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:14.000
Your Highness.

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:24.799
Do you remember the promises we made?

00:01:25.504 --> 00:01:31.044
♪To forget it is to set it free♪

00:01:31.584 --> 00:01:35.200
♪Love's cocoon shatters into snow♪

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:36.599
In the next life and the one after,

00:01:36.599 --> 00:01:37.799
I want to be with you.

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:40.920
Your Highness, you must
agree to all my requests

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:41.799
and keep your word.

00:01:42.340 --> 00:01:44.319
Alright, Xu Tie. I'll listen to you.

00:02:12.384 --> 00:02:17.514
♪Ink stains, memory chains♪

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:20.520
Xu Yu.

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:29.237
♪A dying lamp, a shattered view♪

00:02:30.039 --> 00:02:31.879
Xu Yu!

00:02:31.879 --> 00:02:32.639
Your Majesty.

00:02:33.719 --> 00:02:35.479
You can't be this close to me.

00:02:36.159 --> 00:02:37.199
I'm not going anywhere.

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:40.680
I only need you by my side.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:44.280
I don't want to go back
to the days without you.

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:48.120
Your Majesty,

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:55.039
please accompany me
in smelling these flowers once more.

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:01.159
Alright.

00:03:03.599 --> 00:03:05.599
The weather is lovely today.

00:03:06.479 --> 00:03:07.599
It's a pity...

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:12.000
Once you recover,

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:16.479
I'll smell the flowers

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:19.240
and admire the sky with you every day.

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:24.639
I...

00:03:26.199 --> 00:03:28.479
I have so many more things

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:31.879
to tell you.

00:03:32.719 --> 00:03:33.560
Alright.

00:03:34.719 --> 00:03:35.520
Tell me.

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:37.360
I'm listening.

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:43.479
Your Majesty, you must find
the medicine to save the people.

00:03:45.719 --> 00:03:46.400
Alright.

00:03:48.199 --> 00:03:49.800
After I die,

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:53.400
you must appoint a new Empress.

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:58.520
Don't foolishly remain loyal
to my memory alone, understand?

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:02.240
I might be unhappy about it,

00:04:03.400 --> 00:04:04.120
but

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.719
I don't want people
to criticize me even after death.

00:04:12.199 --> 00:04:12.919
Xu Yu,

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:16.000
in my life,

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:18.879
you are my only Empress.

00:04:22.279 --> 00:04:23.800
As long as I live,

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:26.560
I won't let anyone speak ill of you.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:30.160
And...

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.279
And...

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:37.560
♪Delusions are sharp as blades♪

00:04:37.560 --> 00:04:40.600
- Bound as husband and wife.
- Bound as husband and wife.

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:46.079
No doubt in us.

00:04:49.664 --> 00:04:55.153
♪When love runs deep,
the moonlight fades♪

00:04:56.416 --> 00:05:03.776
♪A cursed fate,
a dream severed over lifetimes♪

00:05:06.439 --> 00:05:06.959
Jinyun!

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.040
Jinyun! There's hope for Xu Yu!

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:10.639
Jinyun!

00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:11.980
Jinyun!

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.000
Jinyun.

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:30.480
Xu Yu.

00:06:55.879 --> 00:06:56.759
- General!
- General!

00:06:57.680 --> 00:06:58.180
General!

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.120
General!

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:01.199
General!

00:07:01.399 --> 00:07:01.959
General!

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:02.560
General!

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.199
How come you're back?

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.319
Weren't you supposed to be with Xu Yu?

00:07:32.199 --> 00:07:32.699
Queen.

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.319
Xiao Jinle has written again.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:37.920
He's quite persistent.

00:07:39.136 --> 00:07:42.720
(Heaven punishes Chen.
Xu Yu has smallpox. Let us unite.)

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:53.000
Xu Yu has contracted smallpox.

00:07:55.319 --> 00:07:56.160
She died.

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:03.439
Since Xiao Jinyun couldn't protect her,

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:05.959
let him join her in death.

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:09.519
Tell Xiao Jinle.

00:08:10.439 --> 00:08:11.560
We agree to cooperate.

00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:22.920
Xiao Jinyun,

00:08:23.639 --> 00:08:24.480
I promise.

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:26.120
I will return safely.

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:27.399
I keep my word.

00:08:28.439 --> 00:08:29.079
Xu Yu,

00:08:30.279 --> 00:08:31.000
so will I.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.279
No doubt in us.

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.240
I keep my word.

00:08:39.279 --> 00:08:40.759
I'll wait for your return.

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:52.559
Xiao Jinyun.

00:08:57.480 --> 00:08:58.440
(Xu Yu,)

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:01.639
(you are my Empress)

00:09:02.879 --> 00:09:04.240
(forever.)

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:07.440
(This palace)

00:09:08.559 --> 00:09:09.840
(has trapped too many people.)

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.879
(Weary birds know their nest.)

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:14.399
(Wanderers seek home.)

00:09:15.039 --> 00:09:16.360
Between us, let there be

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:17.519
no distance

00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:20.360
and no doubt.

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:28.879
That is, bound as husband and wife,

00:09:28.879 --> 00:09:30.600
no doubt in us.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.279
Xu Yu.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:49.240
Xu Yu.

00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:54.759
Your Majesty, you must stop drinking.

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:58.559
Many important court matters
await your attention.

00:10:02.279 --> 00:10:04.840
I can't even protect the one I love.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.679
What good is being Emperor of Chen?

00:10:08.159 --> 00:10:09.039
Your Majesty.

00:10:10.159 --> 00:10:11.879
You are not only Xu Yu's husband.

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:13.840
You are the Emperor of Chen.

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:16.639
Think of the people suffering

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:20.159
and the lands the Xu family
fought and bled for you.

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:26.432
Your Majesty,

00:10:26.919 --> 00:10:28.919
I just received
an urgent military dispatch.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:33.080
What does it say?

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:34.759
The northwest situation is critical.

00:10:35.399 --> 00:10:36.720
Barbarians invaded Yanmen Pass

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.919
with secret aid from Dada.

00:10:38.919 --> 00:10:40.399
Three cities lost in succession.

00:10:40.919 --> 00:10:41.919
General Xu

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:44.159
is severely injured.

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:51.440
Huna has allied with Houyi?

00:10:51.799 --> 00:10:54.480
The Empress treated Huna
with genuine sincerity,

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:56.960
but she betrayed that trust.

00:10:57.600 --> 00:10:59.200
Barbarians truly cannot be trusted.

00:10:59.879 --> 00:11:00.559
Furthermore,

00:11:01.559 --> 00:11:03.759
Prince Ning is spreading news
that the Empress is dead.

00:11:04.360 --> 00:11:07.000
He blames all misfortunes
on Your Majesty angering Heaven

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:08.799
and leads the ministers

00:11:09.080 --> 00:11:11.039
to urge you to perform
a Heaven‑pleasing rite.

00:11:11.639 --> 00:11:12.639
Alright.

00:11:14.159 --> 00:11:15.759
It seems I must make

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:18.480
the Heaven‑pleasing rite
especially grand.

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:21.799
Yes.

00:11:44.279 --> 00:11:45.480
Did you call me here so late

00:11:46.120 --> 00:11:47.639
because of the rite?

00:11:48.759 --> 00:11:49.480
Give me your hand.

00:11:53.399 --> 00:11:53.899
Wait.

00:11:54.799 --> 00:11:56.279
Are you going to take my blood again?

00:11:56.759 --> 00:11:58.399
My blood is very precious.

00:12:04.639 --> 00:12:05.279
This is...

00:12:06.159 --> 00:12:08.480
His Majesty has arranged
everything for the rite.

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:10.159
You will accompany him.

00:12:10.799 --> 00:12:12.120
After taking this pill,

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.399
you will be immune
to sorcery's mental confusion

00:12:14.799 --> 00:12:15.799
for two days.

00:12:16.480 --> 00:12:17.360
What about Jinyun?

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:20.200
His Majesty's was already
placed in his meal tonight.

00:12:21.039 --> 00:12:21.539
By the way,

00:12:22.080 --> 00:12:24.639
I noticed you're not listed
among the rite's preparations.

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:30.559
His Majesty ordered me to guard here.

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:34.960
He is worried that Dada sorcerers allied
with Prince Ning may attack the palace.

00:12:35.720 --> 00:12:37.399
I'm guarding the magic formation here,

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:39.639
so His Majesty can rest easy.

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:46.159
What is this?

00:12:46.879 --> 00:12:48.960
Special knockout incense
I had Jiang Tang prepare.

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:50.919
No matter how skilled the thief,

00:12:51.039 --> 00:12:51.879
they can't resist it.

00:12:52.159 --> 00:12:53.879
The antidote to counter it is inside.

00:13:11.799 --> 00:13:14.200
(As the Son of Heaven,)

00:13:14.519 --> 00:13:15.759
(I ascended the throne)

00:13:16.679 --> 00:13:17.960
(by Heaven's mandate.)

00:13:18.799 --> 00:13:21.120
(However, due to my young age,)

00:13:21.559 --> 00:13:22.960
(I have failed to uphold)

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:24.759
(the virtues of my ancestors.)

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.679
(I disrupted the natural order.)

00:13:27.039 --> 00:13:28.759
(Heaven has punished us)

00:13:28.759 --> 00:13:30.080
(with calamities,)

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:34.000
(all because of
my inadequacy as a ruler.)

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:37.639
(Today, I confess my faults,)

00:13:37.639 --> 00:13:38.919
(and the world shall know.)

00:13:42.200 --> 00:13:43.320
(Disasters)

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:44.759
(are Heaven's warnings.)

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:47.240
(Since I ascended the throne,)

00:13:47.679 --> 00:13:49.919
(I've favored sycophants
and distanced the worthy.)

00:13:50.279 --> 00:13:52.799
(I've prioritized civil officials
over military generals.)

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:54.720
Thus, the empire is destabilized.

00:13:55.320 --> 00:13:57.600
Now, natural calamities plague us,

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:58.720
and war has erupted again.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:01.720
This fault lies with me alone.

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:02.440
Wrong.

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:09.399
Your Majesty's fault is not in this,

00:14:09.639 --> 00:14:12.080
but in being an imposter.

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:14.559
You are the daughter
of the rebellious Xu family,

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.279
Empress Xu Yu!

00:14:25.519 --> 00:14:27.600
You say I'm an imposter?

00:14:28.039 --> 00:14:29.360
Do you have proof?

00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:53.600
What's this?

00:14:54.320 --> 00:14:57.080
The confession written by the Marquis
of Zhenbei before his death.

00:14:57.279 --> 00:14:59.440
Xu Yu conspired with Grand Master Zhang

00:14:59.639 --> 00:15:01.159
to fake His Majesty's poisoning.

00:15:01.159 --> 00:15:03.759
It was actually the final step
of their soul-swapping scheme,

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.320
to make the swap permanent.

00:15:05.559 --> 00:15:07.399
The Marquis of Zhenbei discovered it,

00:15:07.879 --> 00:15:09.279
but Xu Yu killed him.

00:15:09.840 --> 00:15:11.000
He must be insane.

00:15:11.360 --> 00:15:14.799
Now, Xu Yu has used smallpox
to murder His Majesty.

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:18.919
Today, I shall avenge
the true His Majesty!

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:19.919
Prince Ning,

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:22.279
you're treasonous!

00:15:22.279 --> 00:15:23.840
With just this confession,

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:25.399
you want to seize the throne?

00:15:26.200 --> 00:15:27.679
I have irrefutable evidence.

00:15:28.480 --> 00:15:30.039
This is an ancient artifact.

00:15:31.519 --> 00:15:33.679
Any soul-swapped person

00:15:34.279 --> 00:15:36.120
will reveal their true form.

00:15:46.799 --> 00:15:48.960
The mirror still shows Jinyun's face.

00:15:49.519 --> 00:15:51.919
You're accusing others
to hide your own guilt.

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:53.360
(Impossible.)

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:56.159
(Abudu tampered with the copper mirror.)

00:15:56.480 --> 00:15:57.960
(It should only show Xu Yu's face.)

00:15:58.399 --> 00:15:59.720
(How did it go wrong?)

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:01.240
Prince Ning spreads lies

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:02.799
to usurp the throne!

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:04.159
Seize him!

00:16:20.639 --> 00:16:25.823
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

00:16:26.559 --> 00:16:31.122
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

00:16:32.447 --> 00:16:37.862
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

00:16:38.431 --> 00:16:42.975
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

00:16:43.615 --> 00:16:48.879
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

00:16:49.247 --> 00:16:54.924
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

00:16:55.263 --> 00:16:57.279
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

00:16:57.471 --> 00:17:01.215
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

00:17:01.791 --> 00:17:06.463
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

00:17:07.007 --> 00:17:08.767
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

00:17:09.087 --> 00:17:12.703
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

00:17:12.950 --> 00:17:18.477
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪